name: Peperdians of the Galaxy unique limited edition

metadata.name: Peperdians of the Galaxy Full Team
metadata.description:
Courageous and determined frogs protect the Galaxy from numerous threats, including themselves. They stand guard over memes, humor and kindness in the cold emptiness of space.
The team includes:
Pepera, a stealthy assassin with unusual green skin
Sproot - the most chill frog, always stay hydrated
Pocket is a sly kleptomaniac frog known for dragging everything in his pockets
Peper Quill who prefers to be called Frog-Lord and is considered the leader of the team
Drugs Destroyer is a beefy frog known for his love of muscle growth stimulants

Buyer will receive the original digital art 6818x4488 px.
